                        &lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Almost all the time is taken by printing in your &lt;code&gt;print&lt;/code&gt; tests. Printing is expensive. The list building has some cost, too.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/2357112/user2357112&quot; title=&quot;236,891 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;user2357112&lt;/a&gt;
