            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;Why use &lt;code&gt;enumerate&lt;/code&gt; if you&apos;re not actually using &lt;code&gt;itm&lt;/code&gt;? Either change to &lt;code&gt;print(itm, bar[index])&lt;/code&gt; or simply loop as &lt;code&gt;for indx in range(len(foo))&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

